org.matsim.contrib.minibus.replanning

Class ReduceStopsToBeServedRFare

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.matsim.contrib.minibus.replanning.ReduceStopsToBeServedRFare
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StageContainerHandler, PStrategy

    public final class ReduceStopsToBeServedRFare
extends Object
implements StageContainerHandler
    Removes all stops belonging to a demand relation with trips below a certain threshold. Threshold is standard deviation of number of trips or collected fare of all relations twice a scaling factor.
    Author:
    aneumann
